*14. Deportes Quindío        26       4      12      10     29-37   20 
  
Note:  
  
Atlético Junior and Millonarios both with 37 points had to play extra
matches to decide the champion of Torneo Apertura 1976:

First Leg   [Jul 18, Barranquilla]
Junior       4-1  Millonarios

Second Leg  [Jul 20, Bogotá]
Millonarios  4-1  Junior

The last game were not finished due some disturbances in the stadium. Both
teams classified to Final Hexagonal.

   

