Final Hexagonal 

Round 1  [Nov 14] 
Cali         2-1 Millonarios 
Nacional     2-0 Junior 
Caldas       1-0 Quindío 

Round 2  [Nov 18] 
Quindío      0-0 Cali 
Millonarios  1-0 Nacional 
Junior       2-0 Caldas 

Round 3  [Nov 21] 
Nacional     6-0 Quindío 
Junior       1-0 Millonarios 
Caldas       1-3 Cali 

Round 4  [Nov 25] 
Caldas       3-3 Millonarios 
Cali         2-4 Nacional 
Quindío      1-3 Junior 

Round 5  [Nov 28] 
Millonarios  3-2 Quindío 
Nacional     1-0 Caldas 
Junior       0-0 Cali 

Round 6  [Dec 5] 
Junior       4-2 Nacional 
Millonarios  1-0 Cali 
Quindío      1-2 Caldas 

Round 7  [Dec 8] 
Caldas       3-1 Junior 
Nacional     0-0 Millonarios 
Cali         6-1 Quindío 

Round 8  [Dec 12] 
Millonarios  2-0 Junior 
Cali         5-3 Caldas 
Quindío      0-0 Nacional 

Round 9  [Dec 16] 
Millonarios  3-1 Caldas 
Junior       3-0 Quindío 
Nacional     3-0 Cali 

Round 10  [Dec 19] 
Quindío      2-1 Millonarios 
Caldas       0-2 Nacional 
Cali         5-1 Junior 

